{"tid":1558702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日大球場 伊朗球迷都有示威 不滿伊朗政府逼害女性","createTime":"2019-09-10T14:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T11:05:10.000Z","uid":8543,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a237afb866ab55f03d6bb81800a1c8c7e0343ddc","tid":1558702,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"事源： <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-49646879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-49646879&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4Vm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=a4540351\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-49646879&h=e9261722\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-49646879</a><br />\n<br />\nFight for Freedom. Stand with Iran.<br />\n<br />\n伊朗一名女足球迷, 自焚後傷重不治.<br />\n當地傳媒報道, 30歲女事主在二月試圖進入球場, 觀看心愛球隊的比賽, 違反禁止女性進入足球場的法例, 據報她獲悉可能因此被判監半年後, 上星期在法院外自焚受傷, 經搶救後最不治. 報道指, 法庭至今未就案件作出裁決.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20190910174149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20190910174149&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4Vm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=2f21a244\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20190910174149</a>"},{"pid":"c0ca5bc66fa513f0f73d4bbd79b9f744dad74c8f","tid":1558702,"uid":299902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推吖！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUMcWoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUMcWoW.jpg&h=861b949b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekDnzaE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekDnzaE.jpg&h=4e334def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fv6Mgo3.jpg\" data-th