58702,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"中共懷疑係香港策動911恐怖襲擊嘅證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"216b6270d4a9b62319a0db73ea9cfc076708ddd4","tid":1558702,"uid":285924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"今晚係我第一次去現場睇球場。我想講，今晚氣氛真係好好，好團結，球迷支持香港隊一切決定，無論做咩都會拍手，就算射唔中波或對方入波都會話唔緊要。真係做到不割席，希望每一個香港人記住呢刻心情，繼續懷著信念，係抗爭道路上不斷進步同成長。<br />\n<br />\n不指責，不割席。<br />\n毋忘初衷，堅持信念。<br />\n五大訴求，決一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"85902b5d6823fe3fd338a4f048e04aa30c1d1207","tid":1558702,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42318fe9bf748a8469c52672e56230b09f720fd1","tid":1558702,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"Push! Stand with Iran!"},{"pid":"89d0dd27cfa51ecd27ea05adf2c7737c85c015dc","tid":1558702,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"對所有不公義嘅事情都要企出來！<br />\n要想人地stand we us，我地都要stand with them！"},{"pid":"b440f07f3a508d9e15a7476c4451882c0eb03550","tid":1558702,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan